武汉一家三口出院，“一辈子的汗都出完了”。
Wuhan, a family of three discharged, "a lifetime of sweat out."
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 朱轩终于熬过来了！经历半个月的担忧、辛酸和恐惧，以及隔离病房治疗后，截至2月19日，武汉市民赵江的妻子、母亲和宝宝都已出院。
After half a month of worry, bitterness and fear, as well as treatment in the isolation ward, his wife, mother and baby had been released from hospital as of February 19.
“没熬过来时，天天担心。
"Every day I worry when I don't get through.
”2月20日,赵江告诉澎湃新闻，“取得了阶段性的胜利 ”，出院后，一家三口还在不同的地方隔离中。
Zhao told Peng Pai News on Feb. 20 that "there was a phased victory" and that the family was still separated in separate places after being discharged from the hospital.
1月初，赵江的妻子林莉早做准备，买了口罩、酒精。
In early January, Zhao Jiang's wife, Lin Li, made preparations to buy a mask and alcohol.
23日，武汉“封城”，他们连楼都没下过。
23, Wuhan, "closed the city," they did not even under the building.
但当天，林莉的婆婆来访，婆婆有些咳嗽。
But that day, Lin Li's mother-in-law visited, her mother-in-law coughed.
27日，林莉身体酸痛，不久后，她开始发烧。
On the 27th, Lily was in pain. Soon after, she began to have a fever.
29日，她去医院做检查，CT结果显示肺部有感染；当天林莉一家同去做了检查，结果显示，她儿子豆豆和婆婆均双肺感染。
29, she went to the hospital for an examination, CT findings showed lung infection; the same day the LinLi family went to the examination, the results showed that her son and mother-in-law both had lung infection.
2月1日，豆豆确诊新冠肺炎。
February 1, bean confirmed the new crown pneumonia.
为照顾1岁多的宝宝豆豆，赵江进入隔离病房24小时陪护。
In order to care for the 1-year-old baby bean, Zhao Jiang into the isolation ward 24 hours escort.
他不是抵抗力好的人，在医院陪护这段时间，“维C、莲花清瘟、抗病毒口服液、金叶败毒、蛋白粉都在吃，尽量每两小时喝400毫升的水。
He was not a very resistant person. During his stay in the hospital, "vitamin C, lotus rinderpest, antiviral oral liquid, golden leaf sepsis, protein powder are all being eaten. Try to drink 400 ml of water every two hours.
”为了保证娃的营养，除了奶粉米粉，还准备了鸡蛋、面条、燕麦、肉泥、果蔬等。
In addition to powdered milk powder, eggs, noodles, oats, meat and vegetables were prepared to ensure baby nutrition.
孩子睡觉时，赵江基本都在下厨。
When the children sleep, Zhao Jiang is basically in the kitchen.
赵江记录下了豆豆在病房的点滴，也对医患关系有了新的理解：“医护人员拼着命地努力。
Zhao Jiang recorded the dots in the ward, but also a new understanding of the doctor-patient relationship: "Health-care workers strive for life.
同处漩涡的中心，同是基层的工作人员和老百姓，只有更多的理解，才能一起走出去。
At the center of the whirlpool, both grass-roots workers and ordinary people, only more understanding, can go out together.
”2月13日，结合诊断结果，豆豆已痊愈，赵江带他出院回家。
"Feb. 13, combined with the results of the diagnosis, beans have recovered, Zhao Jiang took him home from hospital.
婆婆也恢复得很快，于2月19日出院。
The mother-in-law also recovered quickly and was discharged on 19 February.
在武汉科技大学附属天佑医院住院17天的林莉一直以为自己是症状最轻的那个。
Lin Li, who spent 17 days in Tian You Hospital, an affiliate of Wuhan University of Science and Technology, considered herself the least symptomatic.
直到看到出院小结，她才发现，自己是全家唯一的一个重症，还合并了支原体感染和流感。
It was not until she saw the discharge summary that she discovered that she was the only serious illness in her family, with mycoplasma infection and influenza.
一开始，她的病情不稳定，中间出现过反复发热、呼吸不畅等情况。
At first, her condition was unstable, with recurring fever, shortness of breath and so on.
上了激素和退热栓那天，她感觉，“一辈子的汗都出完了”。
On the day of the hormone and the antifebrile, she felt, "The sweat is gone for life."
早上降了温，但不多会儿，体温又“噌噌噌爬回了37摄氏度以上”。
In the morning the temperature dropped, but soon the body temperature "miso miso up to 37 degrees Celsius."
“我爸从来没哭过的人，我们生病后他大哭一场。
"My dad never cried. He cried when we got sick.
如果他倒下了，我们家真的会崩溃。
If he falls, our family will crumble.
”林莉说，“可是我最终还是熬过来了。
'she said.' But I got through it at last.
这期间所有的医护人员、家人、同事、朋友和同学都给予了我很多的帮助和鼓励，再次拜谢各位！”豆豆和婆婆的好转给了林莉安慰，她决心不做那个“拖后腿的人”，也要努力康复。
During this period, all the medical staff, family, colleagues, friends and classmates have given me a lot of help and encouragement, thank you again!
2月19日，她顺利出院。
On 19 February, she was successfully discharged from hospital.
最难熬的时光已经过去。
The worst of it is over.
目前，他们一家三口在武汉不同的区分开隔离，他们都期待着团聚。
At present, three members of their family are separated in different parts of Wuhan, and they all look forward to the reunion.
（林莉、赵江、豆豆均为化名）本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
(Lin Li, Zhao Jiang, Doudou are aliases) This issue editor Xingtan recommended reading.
